There they are!

174
00:26:48,398 --> 00:26:49,237
Hello

175
00:26:49,238 --> 00:26:50,567
Hello

176
00:26:54,508 --> 00:26:55,627
Here

177
00:26:57,338 --> 00:27:01,247
The intruders don't allow
the Hans to deal with us

178
