Drink!

183
00:27:26,208 --> 00:27:30,307
Look! I'm Mouna Rudo

184
00:27:30,308 --> 00:27:32,397
I killed at Hakaw Supeitei a chief
of the intruders

185
00:27:33,278 --> 00:27:35,077
Mouna Rudo?

186
00:27:35,079 --> 00:27:37,318
You're Mouna Rudo?

187
00:27:37,318 --> 00:27:39,907
Yes, I am

188
00:27:41,288 --> 00:27:43,717
Mouna Rudo!

189
00:28:04,309 --> 00:28:07,638
Chief? Chief?

190
00:28:15,688 --> 00:28:18,277
Where is Mouna Rudo?

191
00:28:24,798 --> 00:28:27,727
I couldn't get him drunk

192
00:29:30,528 --> 00:29:32,427
Wake up!

193
00:29:32,428 --> 00:29:35,397
Those Bununs from Kntabang Clan
are hunting heads

194
00:29:35,398 --> 00:29:36,727
Get up! Let's go!

195
00:29:41,138 --> 00:29:43,737
Let's get out of here! Hurry!

196
00:29:53,718 --> 00:29:57,617
All the human beings on this land

197
