00:34:03,038 --> 00:34:07,007
''Are you my children?''

234
00:34:07,008 --> 00:34:11,777
''Go back! Go back now!''

235
00:34:11,778 --> 00:34:15,947
''You're not true Seediqs''

236
00:34:15,948 --> 00:34:21,977
''You're not qualified to enter
the heavenly home of our ancestors

237
00:34:56,818 --> 00:34:59,057
Run! Come on!

238
00:34:59,059 --> 00:35:00,858
Let's get out of here!

239
00:35:10,868 --> 00:35:13,407
Run, Mouna!

240
00:35:13,408 --> 00:35:14,927
Just go!

241
00:35:17,779 --> 00:35:19,748
Rudo, are you alright?

242
00:35:24,218 --> 00:35:25,477
Father!

243
