their eyes blank

245
00:35:33,228 --> 00:35:39,167
They turn around in shame
and walk though the rugged valleys

246
00:35:39,169 --> 00:35:43,468
They become wailing ghosts
suffering unbearable pain

247
00:35:43,468 --> 00:35:49,837
from all the cuts
by the poisonous crabs along the creek

248
00:35:49,839 --> 00:35:51,608
Mouna..

249
00:35:51,608 --> 00:35:59,277
you must keep the intruders away from our clan

250
00:36:41,458 --> 00:36:46,227
Mouna, do you understand?

251
00:36:46,228 --> 00:36:48,727
Abide by our ancestral dictations

252
00:36:48,728 --> 00:36:54,297
